    9 points\r\n\u2022 Red = 7 points\r\n\u2022 Blue = 5 points\r\n\u2022 Black =
    3 points\r\n\u2022 White = 1 point\r\n\r\n5 Rounds \xD7 3 Arrows = 15 Total\r\nScore
    as high as possible!"
